Titles.eng: Doraemon: Nobita's the Legend of the Sun King
Titles.jpn: 映画ドラえもん のび太の太陽王伝説

Summaries.eng: A Mesoamerican kingdom, called Maya civilisation, is ruled by a queen until an evil witch, Ledina, casts a spell putting her into an eternal sleep. Until the queen awakes, the throne is passed to her young son, Prince Tio.
